* 3 years of experience with Python;
* 3 years of experience with Apache Tomcat;
* 3 years of experience with XML;
* 3 years of experience with JIRA;
* 2 years of experience with Splunk;
* 2 years of experience with Jenkins;
* 2 years of experience with MongoDB;
* 2 years of experience with JQuery;
* 2 years of experience with NodeJS;
* 1 year of experience with React; and
* 1 year of experience with AppDynamics.







